            <h3>Documentation</h3>
            <p>Can the next jammer build on your work? Clear README, commented code, easy to understand and extend.</p>
            <p class="judging-example"><strong>5:</strong> Great README with screenshots/GIF, code comments, clear file structure, easy to extend.<br/><strong>3:</strong> Basic README with instructions, code is readable but sparse comments, no visuals.<br/><strong>1:</strong> No README, cryptic variable names, impossible to understand or extend.</p>
            <div class="score-scale">
